board/index.html
--------------------------------------------------------------------
A MODIFICATION (MPL-2.0 §1.9) of src/index.html from the same upstream
project and commit referenced above. Changes: the build:css/build:js
placeholders (filled by upstream's build step) were replaced with direct
<link>/<script> tags, since this fork ships the unbundled source directly
with no build step; the header title and welcome-screen copy were translated
to English; script tags for board/scripts/20-remote.js and
board/scripts/21-write.js were added, plus a login button (#giteaAuthBtn) in
the header for the latter. Once this fork went web-only: the script tags for
03-storage.js/04-io.js/10-archive.js/11-generate.js and the columnsModal
markup were removed (confirmed unreachable — see the top-of-file comment in
this file for the dependency analysis); the welcome-screen copy was rewritten
to drop the "select a local folder" call to action. A few header buttons
(selectFolderBtn, newTaskBtn, archiveBtn, manageColsBtn, projectSelector,
renameProjectBtn, deleteProjectBtn) and the archiveModal are kept even though
they're now permanently inert — removing them would make unguarded
`document.getElementById(...)` calls in unmodified vendored files throw at
runtime (see the top-of-file comment in board/index.html for specifics). This
file remains available in Source Code Form under MPL-2.0, as part of this
public repository.

