board/scripts/22-assistant.js
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Original work by Paulo Musachio, part of agile-board. Licensed under MIT
(see ../LICENSE). A chat panel calling the
assistant-api backend (assistant/, also MIT/original) to answer questions
(POST /api/ask) or propose board changes as a Gitea pull request
(POST /api/propose). Visible only when logged in (window.__agileBoardWriteMode,
the same flag 21-write.js sets); reads the same stored Gitea token from
localStorage rather than importing 21-write.js's private functions.

